==English==

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|betoken||}}
# To [[signify]] by some visible [[object]]; to show by [[sign]]s or [[token]]s.
# To [[foreshow]] by present signs; to [[indicate]] something future by that which is seen or known.
#: ''A dark cloud often betokens a storm.''

